                    <p>At the University of Minnesota, I completed several major writing assignments covering different topics and subject areas, such as analyzing the usability of everyday objects, exploring current issues in science and technology, and putting together a set of instructions. I’ve included a representative sample of my academic writing to highlight what I’ve learned and taken away from my studies.
