                        </p>
                        <p>
                            This is a heuristic evaluation that I completed for WRIT 4501 Usability and Human Factors in Technical Communication. This was a report in which I applied Jakob Nielsen’s <a href="http://www.useit.com/papers/heuristic/heuristic_list.html" target="_blank">10 web heuristics</a> to the client’s (Hennepin County Library) website. As an evaluator of the <a href="http://www.hclib.org" target="_blank">Hennepin County Library website</a>, I pointed out strengths in the site as well as areas for improvement. The conclusion of the report summarizes the complete evaluation.
                        </p>
